Place your favicon files in this folder:

favicon.ico          — Multi-size ICO file (16, 32, 48px)
favicon-16x16.png    — 16×16 PNG
favicon-32x32.png    — 32×32 PNG
apple-touch-icon.png — 180×180 PNG (iOS)
android-chrome-192x192.png — 192×192 PNG (Android)
android-chrome-512x512.png — 512×512 PNG (Android)
mstile-150x150.png   — 150×150 PNG (Windows tile)

Tools to generate all sizes:
- https://realfavicongenerator.net/
- https://www.favicon.io/

Use a pizza slice or mushroom icon in the brand red color (#C8102E)
on a white or dark background.
